Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女與戰車 OVA第六話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宴會戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決賽真的辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於大家出色的表現 我校成功拿到了優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在戰車道世界中默默無聞的我校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰能想到居然能擊敗如此多豪強學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一次會載入高中戰車道歷史的壯舉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也全靠..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃桃 講太長了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們就開始慶功會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 您請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 不用被廢校真的太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼乾杯吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣而已嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾..乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向校園的風氣乾杯
